<p style="text-align: center;"><span>口干舌燥热汗淌。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>凌晨风凉温度降，</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>还需临时加衣裳。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>夜半值班无声响，</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>寂寞难耐恨更长。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>满天星晨云中藏，</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>期盼霞光出东方。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span>（二）</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span>志愿抗疫上战场</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>小区青年斗志昂，</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>志愿抗疫上战场。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>购菜送菜两头忙，</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>测温上楼好几趟。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>各户垃圾门口放，</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>准时收取不怕脏。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>老弱病残多探望，</span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
