<p style="text-align: center;"><span>解决问题胜儿郎。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>疫情严峻愁茫茫，</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>寂寞孤独显苍桑。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>志愿者们笑脸扬，</span></p>
